  <div align="center"><h5><b>Other Dasas</b><h5></div>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-xs-12"><b>Ayur-dasas:</b> Dasas that are related to longevity and death.</div>
	<div class="col-xs-12"><b>Phalita-dasas:</b> Dasas that are related to general results.</div>
	<div class="col-xs-12">It is considered that Human Mind is governed by Moon.</div>
	<div class="col-xs-12"><b>Nakshatra-dasas:</b> Dasas occured when nakshatra is occupied by Moon.</div>
	<div class="col-xs-12"><b>Raasi-dasas:</b> Dasas occured when Raasi is occupied by Planets.</div>
  </div>
